sentences.english: The first wxdye were the Gaels -came about 600 BC.
sentences.chinese: 第一次高潮是約公元前600年蓋爾人的來臨。

sentences.english: Numerous uniform configurations and merchandise have brought new life to the "Golden Gaels".
sentences.chinese: 衆多的統一配置和商品帶來了新的生活“金蓋爾人”。

sentences.english: Gelda rode the reindeer and went to the Castle of Snow.
sentences.chinese: 蓋爾達騎着馴鹿去了寒冰城堡。

sentences.english: We weren't allowed to speak Gaelic at school.
sentences.chinese: 我們在學校不允許講蓋爾語。

sentences.english: I am in love with the Gelsenkirchen stadium.
sentences.chinese: 我很喜愛蓋爾森基興的球場。

sentences.english: Daguerre partnered with Niépce two years later, beginning a four-year cooperation.
sentences.chinese: 兩年後，達蓋爾和尼埃普斯合作，爲期四年。

sentences.english: Gelda, why are we in such a place like this?
sentences.chinese: 蓋爾達，我們爲什麼會在這樣的地方啊？

sentences.english: Breughel is one of the greatest painters in Netherlands of the 16th century.
sentences.chinese: 勃魯蓋爾是16世紀尼德蘭地區最偉大的畫家之一。

sentences.english: Gail kept her word and returned all the money.
sentences.chinese: 蓋爾履行了她的諾言，把錢如數歸還。

sentences.english: Gheryan town liberated green flags flying in all top destinations.
sentences.chinese: 蓋爾揚解放，高處綠旗飛揚。

sentences.english: Gail Hosey, the mother of the groom, answered a knock at the door to find Coker standing in the doorway.
sentences.chinese: 新郎的媽媽蓋爾弧思打開門時發現寇可站在門前。

sentences.english: Aguerre believes ETA will eventually be eradicated, but it is impossible to say when.
sentences.chinese: 阿蓋爾認爲埃塔終將被消滅，但很難說何時。

sentences.english: Abigail Breslin plays Anna, the younger sister.
sentences.chinese: 阿比蓋爾佈雷斯林次安娜的妹妹。

sentences.english: So Ms. Gail is dialing back her shopping, too.
sentences.chinese: 所以，蓋爾自己也開始減少購物。

sentences.english: Gail was holding out the tablet in trembling hands.
sentences.chinese: 只見蓋爾拿着畫板，手都已經在發抖。

sentences.english: Gelda suddenly was reminded of Kai when she was exposed to the cold wind.
sentences.chinese: 面對凜冽的寒風，蓋爾達突然想起了凱。

definition: the Franks (Germanic people who arrived in Europe from 600 AD and took over France)
